## 5. 核心配置格式

### 5.1 models.yaml

```yaml
profiles:
  main-dev:                        # 主脑（规划/spec/仲裁/合并裁决）
    channel: opencode
    provider: anthropic
    model: claude-sonnet-4-6       # 示例，以实际可用型号为准
  reviewer-kimi:
    channel: http
    provider: moonshot
    model: kimi-k2
    base_url: https://api.moonshot.cn/v1
    api_key_env: MOONSHOT_API_KEY
    price: { in_per_m: 0.0, out_per_m: 0.0 }   # token→成本换算，手工维护
  ds:
    channel: http
    provider: deepseek
    model: deepseek-chat
    api_key_env: DEEPSEEK_API_KEY
```

### 5.2 pipeline 定义（full-auto 完整示例）

```yaml
name: full-auto
autonomy: full                # interactive | gated | full（可被 stage 覆盖）
isolation: worktree           # none | worktree
budget:
  max_cost_usd: 20
  max_retry_steps: 5
stages:
  - id: brainstorm
    type: brainstorm
    models: [main-dev, reviewer-kimi, ds]   # ≥2 个
    mode: debate                            # independent | debate
    debate_rounds: 2                        # 硬上限
    on_unresolved: ask_human                # ask_human | main_dev_decides
    synthesizer: main-dev
    output: brainstorm-report.md

  - id: confirm-brainstorm
    type: human_gate
    prompt: "请确认头脑风暴结论后继续"
    timeout: none               # none = 一直等；或 30m + 默认动作
    # autonomy=full 且无 open_questions 时自动跳过（AutonomyPolicy 决定）

  - id: spec
    type: spec
    model: main-dev             # 通道 A，读代码库
    input: brainstorm-report.md
    output: spec.md

  - id: confirm-spec
    type: human_gate
    prompt: "请确认 spec.md 后继续"

  - id: plan
    type: plan
    model: main-dev             # 通道 B + JSON 校验
    input: spec.md
    output: prd.json

  - id: develop
    type: ralph_loop
    model: main-dev             # 执行手，可换便宜 profile
    max_iterations: 10
    stall_limit: 3
    per_story_fix_limit: 3
    gate:
      checks:                   # 第一层：确定性门禁
        - flutter analyze
        - flutter test
      ai_review:
        enabled: true
        reviewers: [reviewer-kimi]        # 1~2 个，作者 profile 自动排除
        use_agent: false
        fail_on: [blocker]
        fail_threshold: { major: 3 }
        strict: false
```

